{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce measures to hold social media platforms to account for tackling scams",
        "additional_details": "This includes:\r\n- require & enforce ID checks for users\r\n- require reporting & audits\r\n- create an anti-scam taskforce\r\n- raise public awareness\r\n- fund victim compensation\r\n\r\nMany people lose money and trust due to social media scams. I think platforms are failing to act - with scammers operating freely - so we need stronger regulation to hold them accountable, enforce security and protect users. I think it will help prevent financial harm, restore trust and show online safety is a national priority.",
        "background": "I would like the UK government to hold social media platforms accountable for tackling scams on their platforms by requiring them to adopt specific measures.",
